attachments.title: Premium USB to Micro USB Charge & Sync Cable 1.5ft - Black
attachments.text: The USB micro B connector has become the new universal standard connector used on most smartphones and tablets. This premium USB 2.0 cable features a USB A male plug on one end and a USB micro B male plug on the other end. The polycarbonate connector heads are designed to fit through most phone and tablet cases, so you don&#39;t need to remove the case to charge or sync your device.The connector heads measure 0.51&quot; x 0.36&quot; x 0.25&quot; (13.0 x 9.3 x 6.3 mm) on the USB micro B end and 0.51&quot; x 0.55&quot; x 0.25&quot; (13.0 x 13.8 x 6.3 mm) on the USB A end. The gold plated connectors ensure a smooth, corrosion-free connection. The cable is shielded to protect against signal interference and data loss.Features: 100% compliant with USB 2.0 specificationsGold plated connectors ensure a smooth, corrosion-free connectionUltra-thin polycarbonate connector heads fit through most phone/table casesShielded to protect against external signal interference
